<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='739' id='t-739'>Has anyone among you
ever been exposed to tear gas?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5318' id='t-5318'>Tear gas? Anyone?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='8433' id='t-8433'>I'm sorry to hear that, so you might know
