<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='16428' id='t-16428'>with an unpronouncable name:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='18642' id='t-18642'>it's called chlorobenzalmalononitrile.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='21762' id='t-21762'>I made it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='23779' id='t-23779'>It's decades old, but it's becoming
