<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='36753' id='t-36753'>tear gas has two main
but quite opposite effects.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='41026' id='t-41026'>One, it can really burn your eyes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='44168' id='t-44168'>and two, it can also
help you to open them.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='48603' id='t-48603'>Tear gas definitely helped
to open mine to something</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='52192' id='t-52192'>that I want to share
with you this afternoon:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='55932' id='t-55932'>that livestreaming the power
