<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='152897' id='t-152897'>There was no violence.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='154746' id='t-154746'>There was no action scenes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='156835' id='t-156835'>But there was something really exciting,</span>
