<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='168148' id='t-168148'>and I was basically doing the same thing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='170627' id='t-170627'>and all I had was a backpack.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='173403' id='t-173403'>And that was really
