</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='196611' id='t-196611'>And I learned something else,
