<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='205022' id='t-205022'>in the country.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='207216' id='t-207216'>And that really shocked me,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='209758' id='t-209758'>because I was no geek,
