<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226237' id='t-226237'>and the web could be actually used,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='228466' id='t-228466'>already used, as a colossal
and uncontrollable</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='231908' id='t-231908'>and highly anarchical TV channel,
