<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='255392' id='t-255392'>And that sounded revolutionary in my mind.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='257584' id='t-257584'>So for the next couple of years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='259162' id='t-259162'>I started to experiment with
