</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322992' id='t-322992'>But then something happened,
something that wasn't predicted,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='327310' id='t-327310'>that no one could have anticipated.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='329817' id='t-329817'>Street protests started
