<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340227' id='t-340227'>This is a bus.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='342138' id='t-342138'>It's written there, &quot;Theft.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='345102' id='t-345102'>But those kind of manifestations
