<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397638' id='t-397638'>But it wasn't about
the bus fare hike anymore.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400252' id='t-400252'>It was about everything.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='403796' id='t-403796'>The people's demands, their expectations,</span>
